beach-quynhon.jpg?w=80" width="80" height="45" /></a><a href="/fms/environment/161353/central-beaches-safe--says-the-government.html" class="hn-title articletype_5">Central beaches safe, says the government</a><br class="clear" /></div></div><br class="clear" /><div class="body680-bottom1a">
				  
